de.ityx.contex.itag

Class TrainingDocument

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ityx.contex.itag.TrainingDocument
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    @NotThreadSafe
public class TrainingDocument
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Represents a single document in an ITag training corpus. Each TrainingDocument corresponds to exactly one CDocument. The corresponding CDocument is identified by the uri property. It may also be directly linked to in the content property of a TrainingDocument.

    Content may be null. This indicates that the corresponding CDocument was not yet fetched from the database. In this case, the CDocument can still be retrieved by calling ITagModelParameter.fetchTrainingDocument(String, String, long) with the TrainingDocument's URI.
